{
  "video_id": "8KkKuTCFvzI",
  "title": "What makes a good life? Lessons from the longest study on happiness | Robert Waldinger",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12760.0,
      "end_time": 15735.0,
      "text": "What keeps us healthy and happy"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15760.0,
      "end_time": 17320.0,
      "text": "as we go through life?"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18520.0,
      "end_time": 21160.0,
      "text": "If you were going to invest now"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21400.0,
      "end_time": 23960.0,
      "text": "in your future best self,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23120.0,
      "end_time": 26800.0,
      "text": "where would you put your time and your energy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27120.0,
      "end_time": 29536.0,
      "text": "There was a recent survey of millennials"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29560.0,
      "end_time": 34736.0,
      "text": "asking them what their most important life goals were,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34760.0,
      "end_time": 36775.0,
      "text": "and over 80 percent said"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36800.0,
      "end_time": 40936.0,
      "text": "that a major life goal for them was to get rich."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40960.0,
      "end_time": 45296.0,
      "text": "And another 50 percent of those same young adults"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 45320.0,
      "end_time": 47856.0,
      "text": "said that another major life goal"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 47880.0,
      "end_time": 49720.0,
      "text": "was to become famous."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 50960.0,
      "end_time": 52176.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 52200.0,
      "end_time": 58856.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;re constantly told to lean in to work, to push harder"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 58880.0,
      "end_time": 60936.0,
      "text": "and achieve more."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 60960.0,
      "end_time": 64616.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re given the impression that these are the things that we need to go after"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 64640.0,
      "end_time": 66456.0,
      "text": "in order to have a good life."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 66480.0,
      "end_time": 68696.0,
      "text": "Pictures of entire lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 68720.0,
      "end_time": 73936.0,
      "text": "of the choices that people make and how those choices work out for them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 73960.0,
      "end_time": 76839.0,
      "text": "those pictures are almost impossible to get."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 78800.0,
      "end_time": 81136.0,
      "text": "Most of what we know about human life"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 81160.0,
      "end_time": 84616.0,
      "text": "we know from asking people to remember the past,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 84640.0,
      "end_time": 89416.0,
      "text": "and as we know, hindsight is anything but 20/20."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 89440.0,
      "end_time": 93136.0,
      "text": "We forget vast amounts of what happens to us in life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 93160.0,
      "end_time": 96390.0,
      "text": "and sometimes memory is downright creative."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 96800.0,
      "end_time": 101176.0,
      "text": "But what if we could watch entire lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 101200.0,
      "end_time": 104560.0,
      "text": "as they unfold through time?"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 104800.0,
      "end_time": 108560.0,
      "text": "What if we could study people from the time that they were teenagers"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 108800.0,
      "end_time": 110816.0,
      "text": "all the way into old age"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 110840.0,
      "end_time": 114200.0,
      "text": "to see what really keeps people happy and healthy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 115560.0,
      "end_time": 116760.0,
      "text": "We did that."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 117640.0,
      "end_time": 119856.0,
      "text": "The Harvard Study of Adult Development"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 119880.0,
      "end_time": 124640.0,
      "text": "may be the longest study of adult life that&#39;s ever been done."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 125720.0,
      "end_time": 131840.0,
      "text": "For 75 years, we&#39;ve tracked the lives of 724 men,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 133360.0,
      "end_time": 137856.0,
      "text": "year after year, asking about their work, their home lives, their health,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 137880.0,
      "end_time": 142256.0,
      "text": "and of course asking all along the way without knowing how their life stories"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 142280.0,
      "end_time": 143720.0,
      "text": "were going to turn out."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 145280.0,
      "end_time": 148896.0,
      "text": "Studies like this are exceedingly rare."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 148920.0,
      "end_time": 152976.0,
      "text": "Almost all projects of this kind fall apart within a decade"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 153000.0,
      "end_time": 156176.0,
      "text": "because too many people drop out of the study,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 156200.0,
      "end_time": 159950.0,
      "text": "or funding for the research dries up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 159120.0,
      "end_time": 161376.0,
      "text": "or the researchers get distracted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 161400.0,
      "end_time": 165480.0,
      "text": "or they die, and nobody moves the ball further down the field."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 166280.0,
      "end_time": 168536.0,
      "text": "But through a combination of luck"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 168560.0,
      "end_time": 172256.0,
      "text": "and the persistence of several generations of researchers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 172280.0,
      "end_time": 173840.0,
      "text": "this study has survived."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 174520.0,
      "end_time": 179160.0,
      "text": "About 60 of our original 724 men"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 179400.0,
      "end_time": 180335.0,
      "text": "are still alive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 180360.0,
      "end_time": 182536.0,
      "text": "still participating in the study,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 182560.0,
      "end_time": 184600.0,
      "text": "most of them in their 90s."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 185560.0,
      "end_time": 187456.0,
      "text": "And we are now beginning to study"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 187480.0,
      "end_time": 190840.0,
      "text": "the more than 2,000 children of these men."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 191680.0,
      "end_time": 194000.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m the fourth director of the study."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 195400.0,
      "end_time": 200136.0,
      "text": "Since 1938, we&#39;ve tracked the lives of two groups of men."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 200160.0,
      "end_time": 202296.0,
      "text": "The first group started in the study"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 202320.0,
      "end_time": 205160.0,
      "text": "when they were sophomores at Harvard College."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 205400.0,
      "end_time": 207856.0,
      "text": "They all finished college during World War II,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 207880.0,
      "end_time": 210320.0,
      "text": "and then most went off to serve in the war."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 211280.0,
      "end_time": 213416.0,
      "text": "And the second group that we&#39;ve followed"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 213440.0,
      "end_time": 217616.0,
      "text": "was a group of boys from Boston&#39;s poorest neighborhoods,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 217640.0,
      "end_time": 219655.0,
      "text": "boys who were chosen for the study"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 219680.0,
      "end_time": 223160.0,
      "text": "specifically because they were from some of the most troubled"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 223400.0,
      "end_time": 224896.0,
      "text": "and disadvantaged families"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 224920.0,
      "end_time": 227655.0,
      "text": "in the Boston of the 1930s."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 227680.0,
      "end_time": 232280.0,
      "text": "Most lived in tenements, many without hot and cold running water."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 234520.0,
      "end_time": 236416.0,
      "text": "When they entered the study,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 236440.0,
      "end_time": 239376.0,
      "text": "all of these teenagers were interviewed."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 239400.0,
      "end_time": 241616.0,
      "text": "They were given medical exams."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 241640.0,
      "end_time": 245176.0,
      "text": "We went to their homes and we interviewed their parents."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 245200.0,
      "end_time": 247576.0,
      "text": "And then these teenagers grew up into adults"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 247600.0,
      "end_time": 250160.0,
      "text": "who entered all walks of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 250400.0,
      "end_time": 256135.0,
      "text": "They became factory workers and lawyers and bricklayers and doctors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 256160.00000000003,
      "end_time": 258520.00000000003,
      "text": "one President of the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 260160.00000000003,
      "end_time": 264400.0,
      "text": "Some developed alcoholism. A few developed schizophrenia."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 265320.0,
      "end_time": 267616.0,
      "text": "Some climbed the social ladder"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 267640.0,
      "end_time": 270856.0,
      "text": "from the bottom all the way to the very top,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 270880.0,
      "end_time": 274159.0,
      "text": "and some made that journey in the opposite direction."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 275520.0,
      "end_time": 278455.0,
      "text": "The founders of this study"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 278480.0,
      "end_time": 280496.0,
      "text": "would never in their wildest dreams"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 280520.0,
      "end_time": 285560.0,
      "text": "have imagined that I would be standing here today, 75 years later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 285800.0,
      "end_time": 288159.0,
      "text": "telling you that the study still continues."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 289280.0,
      "end_time": 292895.0,
      "text": "Every two years, our patient and dedicated research staff"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 292920.0,
      "end_time": 295976.0,
      "text": "calls up our men and asks them if we can send them"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 296000.0,
      "end_time": 299120.0,
      "text": "yet one more set of questions about their lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 300400.0,
      "end_time": 303616.0,
      "text": "Many of the inner city Boston men ask us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 303640.0,
      "end_time": 307520.0,
      "text": "\"Why do you keep wanting to study me? My life just isn&#39;t that interesting.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 308600.0,
      "end_time": 310976.0,
      "text": "The Harvard men never ask that question."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 311000.0,
      "end_time": 316200.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 320920.0,
      "end_time": 323776.0,
      "text": "To get the clearest picture of these lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 323800.0,
      "end_time": 326736.0,
      "text": "we don&#39;t just send them questionnaires."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 326760.0,
      "end_time": 329216.0,
      "text": "We interview them in their living rooms."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 329240.0,
      "end_time": 332176.0,
      "text": "We get their medical records from their doctors."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 332200.0,
      "end_time": 334695.0,
      "text": "We draw their blood, we scan their brains,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 334720.0,
      "end_time": 336416.0,
      "text": "we talk to their children."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 336440.0,
      "end_time": 341696.0,
      "text": "We videotape them talking with their wives about their deepest concerns."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 341720.0,
      "end_time": 345256.0,
      "text": "And when, about a decade ago, we finally asked the wives"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 345280.0,
      "end_time": 347655.0,
      "text": "if they would join us as members of the study,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 347680.0,
      "end_time": 350376.0,
      "text": "many of the women said, \"You know, it&#39;s about time.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 350400.0,
      "end_time": 351455.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 351480.0,
      "end_time": 353176.0,
      "text": "So what have we learned?"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 353200.0,
      "end_time": 358416.0,
      "text": "What are the lessons that come from the tens of thousands of pages"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 358440.0,
      "end_time": 361496.0,
      "text": "of information that we&#39;ve generated"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 361520.0,
      "end_time": 362719.0,
      "text": "on these lives?"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 363720.0,
      "end_time": 369320.0,
      "text": "Well, the lessons aren&#39;t about wealth or fame or working harder and harder."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 370520.0,
      "end_time": 376816.0,
      "text": "The clearest message that we get from this 75-year study is this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 376840.0,
      "end_time": 382390.0,
      "text": "Good relationships keep us happier and healthier. Period."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 383000.0,
      "end_time": 386816.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve learned three big lessons about relationships."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 386840.0,
      "end_time": 390936.0,
      "text": "The first is that social connections are really good for us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 390960.0,
      "end_time": 393455.0,
      "text": "and that loneliness kills."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 393480.0,
      "end_time": 397136.0,
      "text": "It turns out that people who are more socially connected"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 397160.0,
      "end_time": 400256.0,
      "text": "to family, to friends, to community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 400280.0,
      "end_time": 404976.0,
      "text": "are happier, they&#39;re physically healthier, and they live longer"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 405000.0,
      "end_time": 408376.0,
      "text": "than people who are less well connected."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 408400.0,
      "end_time": 411816.0,
      "text": "And the experience of loneliness turns out to be toxic."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 411840.0,
      "end_time": 416976.0,
      "text": "People who are more isolated than they want to be from others"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 417000.0,
      "end_time": 420216.0,
      "text": "find that they are less happy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 420240.0,
      "end_time": 423176.0,
      "text": "their health declines earlier in midlife,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 423200.0,
      "end_time": 425416.0,
      "text": "their brain functioning declines sooner"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 425440.0,
      "end_time": 429000.0,
      "text": "and they live shorter lives than people who are not lonely."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 430400.0,
      "end_time": 433256.0,
      "text": "And the sad fact is that at any given time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 433280.0,
      "end_time": 437880.0,
      "text": "more than one in five Americans will report that they&#39;re lonely."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 439400.0,
      "end_time": 441696.0,
      "text": "And we know that you can be lonely in a crowd"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 441720.0,
      "end_time": 444376.0,
      "text": "and you can be lonely in a marriage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 444400.0,
      "end_time": 446536.0,
      "text": "so the second big lesson that we learned"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 446560.0,
      "end_time": 449656.0,
      "text": "is that it&#39;s not just the number of friends you have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 449680.0,
      "end_time": 453176.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s not whether or not you&#39;re in a committed relationship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 453200.0,
      "end_time": 457840.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s the quality of your close relationships that matters."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 458560.0,
      "end_time": 463336.0,
      "text": "It turns out that living in the midst of conflict is really bad for our health."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 463360.0,
      "end_time": 467336.0,
      "text": "High-conflict marriages, for example, without much affection,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 467360.0,
      "end_time": 473136.0,
      "text": "turn out to be very bad for our health, perhaps worse than getting divorced."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 473160.0,
      "end_time": 477936.0,
      "text": "And living in the midst of good, warm relationships is protective."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 477960.0,
      "end_time": 481560.0,
      "text": "Once we had followed our men all the way into their 80s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 481800.0,
      "end_time": 484960.0,
      "text": "we wanted to look back at them at midlife"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 484120.0,
      "end_time": 485696.0,
      "text": "and to see if we could predict"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 485720.0,
      "end_time": 489696.0,
      "text": "who was going to grow into a happy, healthy octogenarian"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 489720.0,
      "end_time": 490920.0,
      "text": "and who wasn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 491680.0,
      "end_time": 495896.0,
      "text": "And when we gathered together everything we knew about them"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 495920.0,
      "end_time": 497280.0,
      "text": "at age 50,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 498800.0,
      "end_time": 500616.0,
      "text": "it wasn&#39;t their middle age cholesterol levels"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 500640.0,
      "end_time": 503536.0,
      "text": "that predicted how they were going to grow old."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 503560.0,
      "end_time": 507160.0,
      "text": "It was how satisfied they were in their relationships."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 507400.0,
      "end_time": 511936.0,
      "text": "The people who were the most satisfied in their relationships at age 50"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 511960.0,
      "end_time": 514360.0,
      "text": "were the healthiest at age 80."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 515679.0,
      "end_time": 518856.0,
      "text": "And good, close relationships seem to buffer us"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 518880.0,
      "end_time": 521640.0,
      "text": "from some of the slings and arrows of getting old."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 522480.0,
      "end_time": 526456.0,
      "text": "Our most happily partnered men and women"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 526480.0,
      "end_time": 528535.0,
      "text": "reported, in their 80s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 528559.0,
      "end_time": 531496.0,
      "text": "that on the days when they had more physical pain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 531520.0,
      "end_time": 533480.0,
      "text": "their mood stayed just as happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 534400.0,
      "end_time": 537656.0,
      "text": "But the people who were in unhappy relationships,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 537680.0,
      "end_time": 540616.0,
      "text": "on the days when they reported more physical pain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 540640.0,
      "end_time": 543680.0,
      "text": "it was magnified by more emotional pain."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 544360.0,
      "end_time": 548736.0,
      "text": "And the third big lesson that we learned about relationships and our health"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 548760.0,
      "end_time": 552160.0,
      "text": "is that good relationships don&#39;t just protect our bodies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 552400.0,
      "end_time": 553520.0,
      "text": "they protect our brains."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 554440.0,
      "end_time": 559960.0,
      "text": "It turns out that being in a securely attached relationship"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 559120.0,
      "end_time": 563160.0,
      "text": "to another person in your 80s is protective,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 563400.0,
      "end_time": 565160.0,
      "text": "that the people who are in relationships"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 565400.0,
      "end_time": 569175.0,
      "text": "where they really feel they can count on the other person in times of need,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 569200.0,
      "end_time": 572896.0,
      "text": "those people&#39;s memories stay sharper longer."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 572920.0,
      "end_time": 574415.0,
      "text": "And the people in relationships"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 574440.0,
      "end_time": 577576.0,
      "text": "where they feel they really can&#39;t count on the other one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 577600.0,
      "end_time": 581480.0,
      "text": "those are the people who experience earlier memory decline."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 582520.0,
      "end_time": 585976.0,
      "text": "And those good relationships, they don&#39;t have to be smooth all the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 586000.0,
      "end_time": 589576.0,
      "text": "Some of our octogenarian couples could bicker with each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 589600.0,
      "end_time": 591336.0,
      "text": "day in and day out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 591360.0,
      "end_time": 594536.0,
      "text": "but as long as they felt that they could really count on the other"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 594560.0,
      "end_time": 596376.0,
      "text": "when the going got tough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 596400.0,
      "end_time": 600000.0,
      "text": "those arguments didn&#39;t take a toll on their memories."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 601600.0,
      "end_time": 604336.0,
      "text": "So this message,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 604360.0,
      "end_time": 610560.0,
      "text": "that good, close relationships are good for our health and well-being,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 610800.0,
      "end_time": 613160.0,
      "text": "this is wisdom that&#39;s as old as the hills."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 613400.0,
      "end_time": 616880.0,
      "text": "Why is this so hard to get and so easy to ignore?"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 617560.0,
      "end_time": 619160.0,
      "text": "Well, we&#39;re human."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 619400.0,
      "end_time": 621856.0,
      "text": "What we&#39;d really like is a quick fix,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 621880.0,
      "end_time": 623576.0,
      "text": "something we can get"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 623600.0,
      "end_time": 626360.0,
      "text": "that&#39;ll make our lives good and keep them that way."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 627320.0,
      "end_time": 630656.0,
      "text": "Relationships are messy and they&#39;re complicated"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 630680.0,
      "end_time": 634496.0,
      "text": "and the hard work of tending to family and friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 634520.0,
      "end_time": 637175.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s not sexy or glamorous."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 637200.0,
      "end_time": 640536.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s also lifelong. It never ends."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 640560.0,
      "end_time": 645616.0,
      "text": "The people in our 75-year study who were the happiest in retirement"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 645640.0,
      "end_time": 651456.0,
      "text": "were the people who had actively worked to replace workmates with new playmates."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 651480.0,
      "end_time": 654456.0,
      "text": "Just like the millennials in that recent survey,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 654480.0,
      "end_time": 658960.0,
      "text": "many of our men when they were starting out as young adults"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 658120.0,
      "end_time": 662136.0,
      "text": "really believed that fame and wealth and high achievement"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 662160.0,
      "end_time": 666960.0,
      "text": "were what they needed to go after to have a good life."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 666120.0,
      "end_time": 670296.0,
      "text": "But over and over, over these 75 years, our study has shown"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 670320.0,
      "end_time": 675976.0,
      "text": "that the people who fared the best were the people who leaned in to relationships,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 676000.0,
      "end_time": 679240.0,
      "text": "with family, with friends, with community."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 681800.0,
      "end_time": 683560.0,
      "text": "So what about you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 683800.0,
      "end_time": 686840.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s say you&#39;re 25, or you&#39;re 40, or you&#39;re 60."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 687800.0,
      "end_time": 690760.0,
      "text": "What might leaning in to relationships even look like?"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 691760.0,
      "end_time": 694880.0,
      "text": "Well, the possibilities are practically endless."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 695600.0,
      "end_time": 701696.0,
      "text": "It might be something as simple as replacing screen time with people time"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 701720.0,
      "end_time": 706176.0,
      "text": "or livening up a stale relationship by doing something new together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 706200.0,
      "end_time": 708400.0,
      "text": "long walks or date nights,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 709360.0,
      "end_time": 714216.0,
      "text": "or reaching out to that family member who you haven&#39;t spoken to in years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 714240.0,
      "end_time": 717736.0,
      "text": "because those all-too-common family feuds"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 717760.0,
      "end_time": 719976.0,
      "text": "take a terrible toll"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 720000.0,
      "end_time": 722800.0,
      "text": "on the people who hold the grudges."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 724000.0,
      "end_time": 727920.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d like to close with a quote from Mark Twain."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 729280.0,
      "end_time": 731656.0,
      "text": "More than a century ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 731680.0,
      "end_time": 734295.0,
      "text": "he was looking back on his life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 734320.0,
      "end_time": 735600.0,
      "text": "and he wrote this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 736840.0,
      "end_time": 740536.0,
      "text": "\"There isn&#39;t time, so brief is life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 740560.0,
      "end_time": 745719.0,
      "text": "for bickerings, apologies, heartburnings, callings to account."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 746720.0,
      "end_time": 749536.0,
      "text": "There is only time for loving,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 749560.0,
      "end_time": 753280.0,
      "text": "and but an instant, so to speak, for that.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 754760.0,
      "end_time": 759136.0,
      "text": "The good life is built with good relationships."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 759160.0,
      "end_time": 760376.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 760400.0,
      "end_time": 765840.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}